reviewText:
I love many of the British sitcoms and series from the BBC.
All of these women are fantastic.
needed to add to my british collection
Most of these ladies I've seen in various series which I greatly enjoyed. Led me to explore a few I hadn't seen before.
I have been a fan of British Comedy for a long time. This dvd is a great lesson in the history and the talent of the Great British Ladies of Comedy.
